flowchart LR
    subgraph SRAM
        Q0[Q bank A]
        Q1[Q bank B]
        K0[K bank A]
        K1[K bank B]
    end
    HOST[Host AXI writes]
    PS[Pre-screener]
    PE[PE Array]
    SWITCH[Buffer select bit]

    HOST --> Q0
    HOST --> K0
    HOST --> Q1
    HOST --> K1

    SWITCH -- even blocks --> Q0
    SWITCH -- even blocks --> K0
    SWITCH -- odd blocks  --> Q1
    SWITCH -- odd blocks  --> K1

    Q0 --> PS
    K0 --> PS
    Q1 --> PS
    K1 --> PS
    PS --> PE
    SWITCH -.-> PE
    SWITCH -.-> Host
